{"tid":707905,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"國中班對殉情 遺書留「對不起父母」","createTime":"2018-06-19T03:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:55:05.000Z","uid":177089,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a5643a2af553bc2fa547c29cb6f64cae3524e2","tid":707905,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:21:00.000Z","msg":"〔記者徐聖倫／新北報導〕同為14歲的沈姓少年與林姓少女就讀新北市板橋某國中一年級，2人為同班同學，更是「班對」，但由於雙方父母反對，2人於今晚6時許跳樓殉情。警方調查，今下午1時許，林女就與家人表示要出門找男友，初步懷疑就是相談殉情一事。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，2人升上國中後分到同班，彼此都是遊戲動漫迷，雙方因此互有好感故開始交往，至今已數月，在班上2人看來無異狀，沒想到會發生這種事。<br />\n警方在2人殉情的頂樓發現遺留現場的2支手機，沈、林人分別將遺書存在手機G-mail、記事本中，內容提到，因為父母反對，造成2人非常大的壓力，並表示對不起父母。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/112048_9515cbf402afec084cb8d02489e5c5b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F112048_9515cbf402afec084cb8d02489e5c5b2.png&h=b8689f43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eec8c34a514a659c0b00d8c4b12b2dd2d4047e62","tid":707905,"uid":24310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:59:42.000Z","msg":"創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0a53bcd80549d66e99dfbbeaa879db2d2b2290","tid":707905,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:12:36.000Z","msg":"條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1eddc3b38c3833dc2da256a977466a439473921","tid":707905,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:55:05.000Z","msg":"彼此都是遊戲動漫迷<br />\n<br />\n中二病"}]}